00:00:05.357 --> 00:00:08.080
- Good afternoon everyone.

00:00:08.080 --> 00:00:11.020
I'm Liz Cohen, I'm Dean here
at the Radcliffe Institute,

00:00:11.020 --> 00:00:13.690
and I am delighted
to welcome all of you

00:00:13.690 --> 00:00:17.530
this afternoon to a lecture
by Jane Kamensky, who

00:00:17.530 --> 00:00:19.720
is a professor of
history here at Harvard,

00:00:19.720 --> 00:00:22.540
and the Carl and Lily
