00:00:22.540 --> 00:00:25.540
Director of the
Schlesinger Library.

00:00:25.540 --> 00:00:27.640
Members of the
Pforzheimer family

00:00:27.640 --> 00:00:31.300
have been steadfast supporters
of the Radcliffe Institute

00:00:31.300 --> 00:00:34.420
for Advanced Study
and all of Harvard.

00:00:34.420 --> 00:00:37.810
And I'm delighted that we
have Gary and Mary Pforzheimer

00:00:37.810 --> 00:00:40.300
here with us today in the
audience, so thank you.

00:00:40.300 --> 00:00:45.525
